g.text: Differentiated “pay” and “request” buttons that allows users to choose their action before selecting recipients.
When a recipient is chosen, they are placed into their own seperate card. This allows users to quickly customize payment options per person.
User’s are given a more extensive snapshot of the payment recipi-ent: this provides a bit more peace of mind than just a name.
Newly added recipients inherit the payment amount as the first recipent, but users can easily change the amount per individual.
